The man 'further described the car as being small, clean and possibly a newer model,' the report said. He added the car was a Prius or a Prius-type of vehicle.

Investigators have not speculated on the circumstances of Markel's death in an apparent attempt to withhold information that a guilty party would incriminate themselves with in the event of an arrest.

Indeed, on Wednesday, the police in Florida's state capital released an image of a Toyota Prius and declared it a 'vehicle of interest'.

